{"tid":1469250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"機場感謝祭今日揭幕","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:09.000Z","uid":128430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f7598efbac2c4d21ecf640a8b41405e77b848ee3","tid":1469250,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"經過兩日行動，大家都辛苦而且非常緊張。塞機場呢一招係正確嘅，亦都取得成效。無可否認，行動對來自全球嘅旅客帶來不便，有啲人可能因此滯留左兩日。傳媒亦會反覆播出呢啲畫面，我地急需做啲形象工程<br />\n<br />\n大家考慮下今日搞感謝祭，多謝所有旅客和機場工作人員，派下食物飲品，係離境大堂歡送旅客，多謝佢地嘅體諒同支持。<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩日都係機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤查元朗721 追究警暴811</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"3adf87d0de4eca031e293b97bdc823e58607bf7e","tid":1469250,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3022a129debefe6ad539558e93bb595de7eee384","tid":1469250,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:08:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07d5fcc6e7b491c506daff9af5dfbbf313b7dabf","tid":1469250,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:08:52.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7a87e0eac34b6d358ded04cf94ab3d40f5c68799","tid":1469250,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"33e8dde5e819d385e89b59ea4835539438889ea9","tid":1469250,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"8235d93df753a1c54a1bd3f8877d470880abe20f","tid":1469250,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:09.000Z","msg":"但機管局已取得禁制令"}]}